{"id":279698,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/维权网-医疗纠纷受害人家属到天津市卫生局抗议/","date":"2013-02-18T16:31:08Z","modified":"2013-02-18T16:31:08Z","title":"维权网 | 医疗纠纷受害人家属到天津市卫生局抗议（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员田静民报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>日</span><span>，数名医疗纠纷的死难家属聚集在天津市卫生局、天津市卫生监督所门前，抗议职能部门监管不利，多年诉求无人过问。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>医患纠纷受害人张文艳的父亲张汉因咳嗽去天津市武警医院看病，一小时后突然死亡，该院却收费长达</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>天。其中大抢救两次、吸痰十次、输液</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">500mlx4</span><span>等，并以多收费掩盖死亡真相。然而家属要求鉴定，至今不予进行。医院所在地管辖区，天津市东丽区法院多年不予立案，一起医疗事故部队不管、地方不管，状告近</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>年无果。而逝者女儿张文艳却于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2007</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>日</span><span>，因进京去武警总队告状，回津后被行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>赵俊红的母亲于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月死在天津武警医院，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月案件一审在天津市东丽区法院审理。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>日</span><span>才宣判。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>日</span><span>在天津市第二中级法院立案，进入二审程序《</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(2012)</span><span>二中民四终字第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">647</span><span>号》，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月裁定发回重审。赵俊红说：“要求查清事实，天津武警医院没有在地方卫生行政机关领取《医疗机构执业许可证》不能接诊地方百姓看病，东丽法院法官权欣自己到武警部门调取了部队内部行医许可证，视为对外行医合法。天津武警医院到底有没有对外行医许可证？依法纠正错案，等待审理结果”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>于凤青说：“一张</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">X</span><span>光片就能说明问题，我的右腿部骨折，在武警医院就医，手术时被医生把钢钉打在非骨折部位，造成医疗事故”。至今得不到合法解决。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>陈丽生老人的妻子也是死在天津武警医院，医疗纠纷旷日持久……</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日</span><span>陈丽生在天津市东丽区法院旁听他人案件时，被司法拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>最令人痛心的是一位这个不到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>岁的小女孩，身穿孝衣，抱着妈妈的遗像，站在《妈妈：我不想一个人长大》的横幅下，期盼公正的来到。人们不知这个女孩的姓名，但在为她流泪……</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>死者家属及受害人：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>张文艳</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15022004654 </span></div>\n<div><span>赵俊红</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13132526904</span></div>\n<div><span>张树香</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15620657652</span></div>\n<div><span>于凤清</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15022204635</span></div>\n<div><span>陈丽生</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18920487787</span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-g6jRdSyYA1I/USI9E9bPqoI/AAAAAAAAdU0/paYfEt-eFgY/s1600/IMG_20130216_102041.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"212\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-g6jRdSyYA1I/USI9E9bPqoI/AAAAAAAAdU0/paYfEt-eFgY/s320/IMG_20130216_102041.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-reYL02mE0DI/USI9Fx_bBtI/AAAAAAAAdU8/eEHlDJlhW9g/s1600/%E6%9A%B4%E9%A3%8E%E6%88%AA%E5%B1%8F20130218074517.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"224\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-reYL02mE0DI/USI9Fx_bBtI/AAAAAAAAdU8/eEHlDJlhW9g/s320/%E6%9A%B4%E9%A3%8E%E6%88%AA%E5%B1%8F20130218074517.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"ht